<plot>A young man (Matthew Geriak) loses his leg in a motorcycle accident. While rehabilitating, he takes up cycling. He becomes determined to become the first one-legged person to cycle across the U.S. The movie follows him from his initial rehab through the completion of his historic ride in Boston, detailing all the ups and downs in between.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?159619</url></doc>
